user.biography:
Mālama i ke kai, a mālama ke kai iā ʻoe
Care for the ocean, and the ocean will care for you.

node.text:
RETHINK THE SHARK. 

I’m very honored to be collaborating with @paditv on a limited collection of some of my most memorable shark moments. 💫✨

Did you enjoy watching plastic being sifted from the sand on my recent Reel? That’s was the  wonderful folks at @sustainablecoastlineshawaii- they receive 15% of the proceeds from this collaboration to help continue the incredible work they do. 🤙🤙🤙🤙

See more information on the link in my bio. 

HAPPY ALOHA FRIDAY FRIENDS!
